descript.abstract: This file geodatabase contains datasets that represent municipal boundaries, commissioner district boundaries, precincts and park boundaries. The following links can be used to obtain individual metadata pages: Municipal Boundaries: bdry_city.html 2012 County Commissioner Districts: bdry_commissionerdist2012.html Precinct Boundaries: bdry_precinct.html Park Boundaries: bdry_park.html ECC Dispatch Areas: bdry_dispatcharea.html
descript.purpose: Administrative Boundaries support many functions including Ramsey Countys open data, automated half and quarter section map production, thematic mapping, land records and property assessment and surveying and engineering projects.

timeperd.current:
Data set is current and complete, but updates vary. New versions are released monthly.
bdry_City: content from 2018; maintenance and updates done as needed bdry_CommissionerDist2012: content from 2012; maintenance and updates happen following political re-districting activities bdry_DispatchArea: the dataset is current and complete, but regularly updated to reflect changes bdry_Park: content from publication date; maintenance and updates are irregular bdry_Precinct: content from publication date; maintenance and updates are irregular

idinfo.useconst: None. Please check sources, scale, accuracy, currentness and other available information. Please confirm that you are using the most recent copy of both data and metadata. Acknowledgment of the publisher would be appreciated.

dataqual.logic: Information is visually inspected and corrected as necessary.

horizpa.horizpar: Digitized information is generally +/- 7 feet; some areas have been found to be +/- 30 feet. COGO (coordinate geometry) accuracy generally is +/- 1.0 foot.

procstep.procdesc:
bdry_City: The Municipal [CITIES] boundaries were originally digitized from MNDOT municipality maps. Over time, the boundaries have been edited to better match the parcel data maintained by the county.
bdry_CommissionerDist2012: The Ramsey County Commissioner Districts were created as part of a redistricting process following the 2010 census.
bdry_DispatchAreas: Created by Ramsey County Emergency Communications with consultation from the Public Safety agencies serving in Ramsey County.
bdry_Park: The parks boundaries are compiled from a variety of sources including Ramsey County Parks & Recreation department and several municipalities.
bdry_Precinct: The Ramsey County Precincts were created as part of a redistricting process following the 2010 census and subsequent city resolutions.

attracc.attraccr: Attributes are populated from a compilation of records and information from various state, county and city offices, and other sources. Accuracy may vary by source, but domains are used wherever possible to increase accuracy.
